02_chi_verbose.patch -- this patch makes CAPS2 output values related to
its chi^2 test. It was temporarilly used when preparing AutoCoEv's own
Chi^2 test functions in chi2.sh.

extraVerbose.patch -- this patch will save the contents of the totaltemp
vector to a text file. This may be desired if you wish to inspect the
simulated data. Be warned that the size of the generated files can be
hundreds ot MB or even more!!

[!!! WARNING !!!]
DO NOT USE THE PATCH WITH AUTOCOEV -- YOU WILL FILL YOUR HARD DRIVE.
